 create files in the working directory without an explicit path definition
 in the filename
In-Reply-To: <9673FE69-EDBB-4031-8CDE-BA3C79E0B568@ifom.eu>
References: <D1529497-BC59-4C4C-A3DB-A1699C671405@ifom.eu>
 <CAANT7+VrGfxjCmZ2=bMHoW3fMGbkOmV0_XU4wdhCr0mVAF8X4g@mail.gmail.com>
 <BN8PR12MB3188CE36A525EABEF45EC239F9430@BN8PR12MB3188.namprd12.prod.outlook.com>
